                <h1>Salsa Music: The Heartbeat of Latin Dance</h1>
                <p>Salsa music is a vibrant genre that blends diverse rhythms, typically featuring brass instruments, percussion, and captivating melodies. Originating in the Caribbean and popularized in Latin dance halls, salsa's infectious beats encourage movement and joy. It's not just music; it's a cultural celebration uniting communities through dance and rhythm.</p>
